cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with 3D reconstruction and semantic trait measurement using RGB or RGB-D data captured by a camera. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses automation of the measurement process in horticulture. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of novel detection and fitting algorithms. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with automated measurement and semantic information extraction. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with 3D reconstruction and merging of partial reconstructions.
